y\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was he who helped me out, he was really my friend today.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my friend\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ground was perhaps a little stickier than we expected, which explains the time-faults a bit,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ground\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"the time-faults\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of pressure on these three days.\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"these three days\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have been talking about nothing else for so long.\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the most pressure I have felt in my career, definitely, but that's a positive thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most pressure\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive thing\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan has risen from fifth to the bronze medal position after the Olympic cross-country, on a team score of 93.80.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1790, \"end\": 1795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7835508694082518, \"rank\": 0.27614599824168024, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japa