on Street\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grafton_Street\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grafton_Street\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cekatinka\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"6.4 time-penalties\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"their 34.5 dressage\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"Kazuma Tomoto\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"Vinci\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"De La Vigne\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kazuma was \\\"really pleased and proud\\\" of 15-year-old Vinci De La Vigne, who is owned by the Japanese Equestrian Federation.\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2191, \"end\": 2199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_Japan\", \"score\": 0.7255994621063528, \"rank\": 0.22301125832911944, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kazuma\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"15-year-old Vinci De La Vigne\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He knows everything; what he needs to do, what I want him to do.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's an absolute professional horse, especially in the big events.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an absolute professional horse\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"the big events\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At home, he's like a lazy boy but in a big atmosphere he's like, 'Come on it's my time', so he was fantastic today,\\\" said Kazuma.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phr